.Dd April 16, 2016
.Dt PFD 1
.Os disputils
.Sh NAME
.Nm pfd
.Nd print monitor containing the focused window
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm pfd
.Op Fl w Ar wid
.Sh DESCRIPTION
Print the ID of the monitor containing
.Ar wid
or the currently focused window (if
.Ar wid
is not specified) to
.Dv stdout .
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Nm
acts on the X display specified by the
.Ev DISPLAY
variable.
